results.description:
I am committed to healing the impact of divorce in this country, one woman, on family at a time.

Women are the center of the home and family.  When we are healed, whole, and well, so are our children, so are our families, and so are any future romantic partnerships we choose to create.

If you have experienced being:
- A woman feeling alone, sad, and unsupported trying to heal the pain of separation and divorce;
- A mom trying to rear healthy, resilient children without passing along your struggles, hurts, and mistakes;
- Frustrated with your relationship past and wanting to build a different relationship for your future;
- Committed to creating a great co-parenting relationship with the father of your children and not sure where to begin;

Then it’s time! It’s time for you to lovingly embrace your hurt, heal your life and become the amazing woman you were born to be.

If you see yourself anywhere in this description, then this group is for you! This group is for those women who are ready to experience their lives as healed and transformed. This group is for women who want to learn and practice trusting  themselves and creating an amiable relationship with the father of their children; for women who want to rear their children to be brilliant and solid citizens, that are emotionally and spiritually well balanced; and dating and relating to men from a place of peace and power. This group is for women to help heal themselves and lend their healing energy to others. This group is to help women feel heard, known, and honored. This group is a safe space to share your hurt and shed your tears. This group is a place to express your joy and stand in your power as a loving feminine presence.

If you see yourself as ready to embrace becoming a dynamic woman, ready to do the work, ready to let go of your past, then join us and we heal the world, one woman, one family at a time.
